  长效及短效糖皮质激素在闭角型青光眼急性发作期联合降眼压药物对眼内压的临床评估
  Clinical Evaluation of Long Acting and Short Acting Glucocorticoid on Intraocular Pressure during Acute Episode of Angle-Closure Glaucoma Combined with IOP Drugs
 
